@page "/"

<PageTitle>PaycheckCalc — Home</PageTitle>

<h1>💰 PaycheckCalc</h1>

<p class="lead">
    A paycheck calculator covering all 50 US states plus DC using 2026 tax
    tables. Built with <strong>Blazor Web App</strong> and powered by the
    shared <strong>PaycheckCalc.Core</strong> calculation engine.
</p>

<div class="card mt-4 mb-4">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">✅ What this calculator does</h5>
        <ul class="mb-0">
            <li>Gross pay from hourly rate, regular hours, and overtime</li>
            <li>Federal income tax — IRS Publication 15-T (2026) percentage method</li>
            <li>FICA — Social Security (6.2%, cap $184,500) and Medicare (1.45% + 0.9% surcharge)</li>
            <li>State income tax — all 50 states + DC with state-specific calculators</li>
            <li>Local taxes — PA EIT/LST, NYC, Ohio RITA/CCA, MD counties</li>
            <li>Pre-tax and post-tax deductions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<a href="inputs" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Open Inputs →</a>
